item.title: Prayer bpn4911 in Vanuatu
item.description: O Yu Kaen Masta! Olgeta we i wok long Yu i kam tugeta long miting ia, mo oli lukluk long Kingdom blong Yu. Olgeta i nidim tu mas ol help mo ol blesing blong Yu. O God! Soemaot mo mekem i kam klia ol saen we i stap insaed long ol tru samting long laef, we i soem se Yu Yu wan nomo. Soemaot mo mekem i kam antap ol gudfala fasin we Yu bin mekem i stap haed insaed long ol man.
